# ============================================
# WORKBOT BRAIN - GITIGNORE
# ============================================
# Framework files (_system, _templates, _frameworks) ARE committed.
# Content files (your actual knowledge) are NOT committed.
# This keeps the brain reusable across clones.
# ============================================

# --- CONTENT DIRECTORIES ---
# Tracked locally for history. Not pushed to remote.

# --- OBSIDIAN WORKSPACE STATE (device-specific) ---
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
.obsidian/plugins/
.obsidian/themes/

# --- QMD SEARCH INDEX (derived data, rebuild with `qmd update && qmd embed`) ---
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-wal
*.sqlite-shm

# --- DEFAULT OBSIDIAN FILE ---
Welcome.md

# --- OS / EDITOR JUNK ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~
